snippet.title: Jason Momoa, James Wan, and Amber Heard at Aquaman Fan Event 2018
snippet.description:
[Originally uploaded on December 16, 2018 on FB: Glenmarc]
I got to meet the stars of the Aquaman movie!
Sharing this short video on what went down at the Aquaman fan event (December 11, 2018, SM Mall of Asia Music Hall) where I got to meet Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, and director James Wan. Thrilled to have all three of them sign my Funko POP Aquaman figure too.
Big thanks to Warner Bros Ph for the special invitations for me and my Justice PH teammates.
